Planning permission for the city of Paris in 2016

Data processing

The data that you see on the map come from the city of ParisData, the Open Data initiative from the city of Paris as they were on 12-07-2017: autorisations-durbanisme-h.csv.

After some cleanup to remove invalid characters, I only kept the latitude, longitude and the year of the permission was asked.

library(dplyr)
library(tidyr)

cleaned_data <- read.csv2('data/autorisations-durbanisme-h-clean.csv',
                          quote = "",
                          stringsAsFactors = FALSE,
                          encoding = 'utf-8')
filtered_data <- cleaned_data %>%
    filter(geom != '') %>%
    filter(annee_depot == 2016) %>%
    select(geom) %>%
    separate(geom, c('lat', 'long'), ', ', convert = TRUE)
